title: Use forks to share control of knowledge!
pid: 337e7d6f-e9c5-44a2-8747-1d48c7b8453c
body: |2-
  This is [[https://github.com/JeffreyBenjaminBrown/skg][Skg]]'s novel contribution to history.
  You read it here first.
  You and another can both "control" a body of ideas,
  such that conflict is impossible.
  I'll explain how in a second.
